Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.81,0:00:05.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,終於
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.52,0:00:07.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,終於
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.11,0:00:12.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,爸媽終於給我買手機了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.48,0:00:00.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,——op——
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.62,0:01:46.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,手機
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.25,0:01:49.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,保存好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.59,0:01:51.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,謝啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.84,0:01:52.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.35,0:02:02.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你買手機了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.89,0:02:03.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.39,0:02:06.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那是最新款嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.73,0:02:08.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我也正準備要買這款
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.10,0:02:10.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我可以摸摸看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.31,0:02:11.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.52,0:02:15.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 還挺輕的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.74,0:02:18.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,為了今天絞盡腦汁才想出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.36,0:02:21.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,用手機捉弄高木同學的計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.32,0:02:25.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天我就要用它戰勝高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.20,0:02:28.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,誒 原來是這樣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.21,0:02:31.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,謝謝你 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.83,0:02:33.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.10,0:02:42.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.10,0:02:43.85,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.43,0:02:46.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.36,0:03:01.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我原本以為高木同學會問我要郵箱地址
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.45,0:03:03.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.33,0:03:05.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.25,0:03:08.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.37,0:03:11.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.83,0:03:14.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣下去就沒法實施計劃了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.59,0:03:21.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我主動去問高木同學不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.47,0:03:25.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼我沒有注意到這麼簡單的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.43,0:03:27.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.64,0:03:28.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.85,0:03:30.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.35,0:03:35.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,把你的郵箱地址…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.15,0:03:39.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,抱歉 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.15,0:03:45.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 我為什麼要這麼緊張 冷靜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.95,0:03:48.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,只是找高木同學要她的郵箱地址而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.96,0:03:55.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,難道我正在問女生要郵箱地址嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.25,0:04:00.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,感覺這樣…有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.13,0:04:02.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,像是那個啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.01,0:04:05.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我說 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.85,0:04:08.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你有什麼事情想要問我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.06,0:04:09.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不不不
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.35,0:04:10.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.43,0:04:11.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.86,0:04:19.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我還以為你想問我要郵箱地址呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.19,0:04:21.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,暴露了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.11,0:04:24.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 不如說這正是機會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.82,0:04:27.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這個問題只要回答Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.24,0:04:28.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我就能拿到她的郵箱地址了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.04,0:04:30.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你大意了啊 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.12,0:04:36.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,其實你說的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.46,0:04:38.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那你剛才為什麼要糊弄過去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.42,0:04:40.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,難道你害羞了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.88,0:04:42.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.17,0:04:44.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這個高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.68,0:04:47.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 才不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.77,0:04:53.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.73,0:04:56.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是有什麼事 連繫起來就方便多了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.15,0:04:57.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,例如呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.36,0:04:58.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就是有什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.15,0:05:01.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你還問到了誰的郵箱地址
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.49,0:05:07.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,木村和高尾 還有中井
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.37,0:05:08.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,其他的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.20,0:05:10.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,還沒問
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.66,0:05:14.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒錯啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.12,0:05:16.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學是我問的第一個女生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.25,0:05:19.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,所以快點 快點把郵箱地址告訴我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.17,0:05:23.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你想和我交換郵箱地址嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.80,0:05:31.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,才沒有 我只是想用郵件來捉弄高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.31,0:05:33.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,才不是像你想的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.35,0:05:36.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我真的一點奇怪的事情都沒有想過…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.99,0:05:48.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我就知道會是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.66,0:05:57.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,雖然你想捉弄我的計劃泡湯了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.75,0:05:59.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但我們還是來交換郵箱地址吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.05,0:06:08.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.80,0:06:12.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,作為捉弄我的賠禮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.22,0:06:14.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你下週要幫我值日
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.35,0:06:16.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我才沒有捉弄你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.06,0:06:18.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,還沒捉弄到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.40,0:06:22.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是 如果沒暴露的話就會捉弄我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.44,0:06:26.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那就這麼定了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.16,0:06:31.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,在這之前 我們到家再聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.25,0:06:39.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,在這之前？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.33,0:06:46.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,難道我在家裡也會被她捉弄嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.43,0:06:51.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,想要手機
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.14,0:06:55.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是昨天和媽媽說的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.35,0:06:58.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,她說我要買手機還太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.39,0:07:00.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這麼突然她肯定會這樣說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.94,0:07:02.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你無論幹什麼都很突然呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.90,0:07:04.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,才不突然好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.82,0:07:07.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我很久以前就想要了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.61,0:07:09.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,很久以前是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.32,0:07:10.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.91,0:07:14.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,大概一週前吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.62,0:07:18.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,看你這樣子 應該是三天前吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.91,0:07:21.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,無論怎麼樣 都太突然了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.08,0:07:25.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}那是什麼呀 犯規了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.84,0:07:26.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.88,0:07:28.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}超級大狸貓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.39,0:07:34.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不過 現在有手機的同學也越來越多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.60,0:07:37.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我也有點想要了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.39,0:07:40.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,對吧 你也想要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.31,0:07:43.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,大家一起去拜託媽媽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.60,0:07:45.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,早苗也很想要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.56,0:07:47.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 我不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.61,0:07:49.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,誒 為什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.49,0:07:51.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一起來發郵件嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.45,0:07:52.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.41,0:07:55.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因為我已經有一部了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.99,0:07:58.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼你會有手機
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.37,0:08:01.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因為社團有時會弄得很晚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.79,0:08:02.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,所以爸媽讓我帶著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.29,0:08:07.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,話說這種事情你倒是告訴我們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.84,0:08:09.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.38,0:08:12.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是說早苗也有的話說不定就會買給我了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.51,0:08:14.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這個主意不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.09,0:08:16.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我也這樣跟家裡說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.35,0:08:18.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣一來就能得到手機了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.39,0:08:20.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一起來發好多郵件吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.27,0:08:23.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我想在睡覺前玩接龍或者猜謎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.44,0:08:25.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,誒 好麻煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.86,0:08:29.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就是因為你這麼說 你爸媽才不給你買的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.48,0:08:31.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那我們來講恐怖故事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.03,0:08:34.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你是最膽小的那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.11,0:08:36.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.87,0:08:38.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.62,0:08:40.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我們來試一試嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.70,0:08:45.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,有天晚上 一個陌生的電話號碼打了進來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.04,0:08:47.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,接通電話的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.21,0:08:50.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,聽到的是一陣呻吟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.30,0:08:56.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,慌慌張張地把電話掛斷之後 對方卻再也沒有打過來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.39,0:08:56.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}太好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.80,0:08:59.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是因為太過在意 試著回撥了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.01,0:09:01.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,誒 為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.56,0:09:04.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,然而 什麼聲音也沒有聽見
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.02,0:09:06.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.15,0:09:08.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.86,0:09:12.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不知為何 電話費竟高達十萬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.24,0:09:17.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an7}「架空請求」，日本的電信詐騙的一種
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.24,0:09:17.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,太可怕了 電信詐騙太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.03,0:09:20.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,明明是由加莉更可怕好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.58,0:09:26.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,恐怖故事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.55,0:09:33.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,早上好 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.13,0:09:35.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.84,0:09:39.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你遵守之前的約定了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.93,0:09:41.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.27,0:09:48.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我來幫你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.52,0:09:49.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.95,0:09:59.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你好像很睏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.41,0:10:02.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.08,0:10:07.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你熬夜看了錄下來的百分百單相思嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.96,0:10:09.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,才不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.38,0:10:10.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.71,0:10:12.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那是為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.05,0:10:14.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,有點事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.01,0:10:17.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,和班上的男生聊短信了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.51,0:10:19.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.64,0:10:20.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,聊了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.80,0:10:25.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,咦 高木同學難得對這個話題感興趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.06,0:10:28.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.85,0:10:31.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,第一次有手機的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.86,0:10:34.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,和別人聊短信真的很開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.36,0:10:36.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我當時也是聊到不能自拔的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.53,0:10:40.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,然後 家人就叫我適可而止
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.12,0:10:45.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,和高木同學聊短信的人 是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.16,0:10:48.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.50,0:10:50.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是和班上的女生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.79,0:10:51.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.59,0:10:57.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,冷靜 之前也有過這種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.84,0:11:01.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,最後一次和我兩個人一起騎車的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.39,0:11:02.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是我爸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.31,0:11:05.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.97,0:11:07.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是和你爸聊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.18,0:11:09.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我才不會和爸爸聊短信啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.69,0:11:11.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那倒也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.65,0:11:13.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你想知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.11,0:11:17.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.82,0:11:21.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是西片告訴我男孩子之間會聊些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.61,0:11:22.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我就告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.78,0:11:25.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.12,0:11:29.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.29,0:11:31.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我有個一石二鳥的好辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.79,0:11:36.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學 你也就只有現在能悠哉悠哉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.30,0:11:39.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,其實呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.67,0:11:44.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,昨天男生們互發有趣的視頻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.55,0:11:46.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎樣的視頻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.93,0:11:49.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,很好很好 如我所料
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.06,0:11:57.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這是木村發來的網址
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.00,0:12:15.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,把這個害我昨晚睡不好的視頻…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.09,0:12:21.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你給我發了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.05,0:12:24.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,有可愛動物的視頻網站
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.55,0:12:27.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,難不成是色情網站呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.05,0:12:28.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.89,0:12:33.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.23,0:12:36.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣啊高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.15,0:12:38.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,害怕得說不出話來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.99,0:12:42.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.36,0:12:44.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.11,0:12:47.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片你總是在看這種東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.62,0:12:52.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.45,0:12:53.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,等等 那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.21,0:12:57.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我給你發的不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.75,0:12:59.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我只是問一下而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.88,0:13:04.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好吧 看看西片給我發的視頻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.14,0:13:08.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,又是這樣 高木同學這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.77,0:13:13.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的是動物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.27,0:13:16.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真可愛啊 這個是山羊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.02,0:13:19.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,很好很好 她放鬆警惕了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.90,0:13:21.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,快到時間了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.40,0:13:25.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好 就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.57,0:13:27.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,被嚇得魂飛魄散吧 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.78,0:13:32.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.71,0:13:36.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不對 你不害怕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.92,0:13:37.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,害怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.92,0:13:41.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因為是在早上看的 所以也沒那麼害怕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.55,0:13:47.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,確實是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.76,0:13:50.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,原來在發這種東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.06,0:13:52.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,男生真有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.85,0:13:57.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學會和誰聊天 聊些什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.35,0:14:01.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我聊的只是普通的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.86,0:14:03.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣根本不算回答嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.03,0:14:05.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.36,0:14:06.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,讓我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.99,0:14:10.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,對方名字的首字母是「i」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.62,0:14:11.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,「i」？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.33,0:14:12.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,「i」…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.70,0:14:16.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是石井同學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.33,0:14:17.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.08,0:14:19.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,「i」之後是「to」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.96,0:14:20.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,「ito」…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.04,0:14:22.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,「ito」？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.54,0:14:23.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼 是伊藤嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.59,0:14:24.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那個男生？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.59,0:14:27.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不是班上的伊藤啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.80,0:14:31.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,然後 最後一個字是「ko」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.26,0:14:33.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,「ito」…「ko」？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.26,0:14:33.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an7}日語中的「itoko」是指表或堂兄弟姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.97,0:14:37.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.73,0:14:47.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,九十七
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.49,0:14:48.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,九十…八
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.45,0:14:51.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,九十…九
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.70,0:14:54.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可惡的高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.58,0:14:57.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我還以為今天肯定能捉弄到她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.33,0:15:00.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,結果反過來被捉弄了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.34,0:15:06.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不行 今天還沒結束
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.55,0:15:11.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,早上不奏效 晚上發給她就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.51,0:15:14.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,回家的時候木村發給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.76,0:15:16.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,更恐怖的視頻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.81,0:15:19.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,雖然因為太可怕了 我還沒看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.35,0:15:22.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就把這個發給高木同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.19,0:15:25.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.86,0:15:30.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不會又是什麼要讓我做俯臥撐的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.37,0:15:35.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,喂 是西片嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.87,0:15:36.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.33,0:15:39.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我覺得差不多到時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.50,0:15:40.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.42,0:15:43.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,發恐怖視頻給我的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.50,0:15:45.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.01,0:15:49.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這個高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.26,0:15:52.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,以為這樣就能揭露我的計劃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.68,0:15:53.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,勝負還…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.68,0:15:56.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,「你好好期待著掛斷電話之後會發生什麼吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.47,0:16:00.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你是這樣想的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.85,0:16:02.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 沒這麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.85,0:16:04.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.90,0:16:06.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,千真萬確
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.74,0:16:11.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那你差不多要睡了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.91,0:16:15.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯 應該吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.99,0:16:16.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.53,0:16:19.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我也差不多要睡覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.79,0:16:22.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.25,0:16:27.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,感覺有點奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.67,0:16:32.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我還是第一次在晚上和西片說話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.18,0:16:34.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,有點小心動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.43,0:16:39.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那明天見 晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.93,0:16:42.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.44,0:16:50.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.24,0:16:52.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.61,0:16:53.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你還沒掛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.16,0:16:56.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我說電話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.78,0:16:58.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學來掛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.37,0:17:02.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是我打給你的 西片來掛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.04,0:17:04.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.42,0:17:07.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那我們數一二 一起掛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.63,0:17:08.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.71,0:17:09.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一 二
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.63,0:17:14.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你個騙子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.09,0:17:17.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學才是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.53,0:17:36.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.91,0:17:38.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今晚也睡不著了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.91,0:17:41.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,照片
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.87,0:17:47.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,貓在打架
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.75,0:17:50.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你等一會 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.80,0:17:52.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你要幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.88,0:17:54.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好 很好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.84,0:17:57.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,保持這樣 保持這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.72,0:18:01.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好 按快門的好機會
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.22,0:18:05.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可惡 只拍到了牆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.52,0:18:08.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你怎麼了 突然拍什麼照片啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.81,0:18:15.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我們男生現在在比誰能拍出更有趣的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.99,0:18:18.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,現在第一名是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.53,0:18:24.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,木村的這張遙遙領先
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.70,0:18:27.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這張的衝擊感很強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.37,0:18:29.08,Takagisan-huamian,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs100\pos(500,212)}超市
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.37,0:18:29.08,Takagisan-huamian-1,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fn@楷体\an7\frz270\pos(592,722)}大狸貓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.71,0:18:31.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,有趣的照片嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.17,0:18:36.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學 讓我拍拍你的鬼臉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.76,0:18:40.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那張絕對能比過超級大狸貓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.05,0:18:45.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是西片什麼都願意做的話就行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.22,0:18:47.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼都？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.27,0:18:50.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就是什麼都答應我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.94,0:18:53.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.23,0:18:58.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,明明這裡就有一位能衝擊第一名的種子選手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.95,0:18:59.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.33,0:19:07.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學 你的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.79,0:19:12.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,明明給你拍照機會了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.34,0:19:14.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,再 再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.88,0:19:15.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.05,0:19:19.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.26,0:19:20.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,她可是高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.68,0:19:23.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嚐到甜頭之後肯定還會再來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.64,0:19:27.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,現在就裝作一副失落的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.27,0:19:29.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.39,0:19:30.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你看吧 她來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.27,0:19:31.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,拍照的機會到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.44,0:19:40.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是玩具蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.03,0:19:41.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,拍的不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.03,0:19:42.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.12,0:19:44.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你剛才拍我了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.24,0:19:47.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,等等 快刪掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.49,0:19:49.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不要 我好不容易才拍到的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.25,0:19:53.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你要是什麼都願意做的話 我就把它刪掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.34,0:19:57.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可惡的高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.13,0:19:59.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這個計劃也太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.30,0:20:01.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 真是拍到好照片了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.05,0:20:03.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片也要看看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.76,0:20:04.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我就不必了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.18,0:20:06.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你看你看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.23,0:20:11.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,還是連拍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.56,0:20:12.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,很不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.89,0:20:14.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這表情變化
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.86,0:20:23.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可惡的高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.82,0:20:25.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.03,0:20:30.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我要把你這副咧著嘴笑得像個傻子一樣的表情拍下來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.62,0:20:33.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你肯定會羞得抬不起頭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.88,0:20:38.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,拍好看了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.67,0:20:41.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣一來就扯平了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.34,0:20:44.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哪裡扯平了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.55,0:20:49.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我把這張刪掉 你也把那些刪了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.02,0:20:51.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我不刪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.56,0:20:54.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,所以你不刪我的照片也行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.60,0:20:58.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 我不是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.49,0:21:05.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,再見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.28,0:21:08.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,她心情真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.33,0:21:13.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,明明我一張有趣的照片也沒拍到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.96,0:21:16.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.37,0:21:19.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我的照片 不可以給別人看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.25,0:21:23.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我會害羞的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.85,0:21:34.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不不 我怎麼會給別人看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.35,0:21:37.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不知道別人會說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.48,0:21:40.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,太危險了 還是刪了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.15,0:21:48.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,她說她會害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.45,0:21:52.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,說不定哪天和她談判的時候能用到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.96,0:21:57.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,先留著吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.43,0:00:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,——OPJP——
