Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.17,0:00:41.56,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}在校園的庭院 第一個發現你的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.60,0:00:49.82,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}今天要和你說些什麼呢 即便是想著這些也是一種樂趣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.86,0:00:52.78,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}窗簾隨風起舞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.57,0:00:58.16,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}不經意地投入一束陽光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.24,0:01:02.04,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}你那美麗的容顏笑起來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.29,0:01:05.96,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}羞得我抬不起頭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.87,0:01:14.05,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}風兒喧囂 似要吹散考試的憂鬱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.17,0:01:22.35,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}吶 我想要和你一起 立下兩人的秘密約定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.72,0:01:27.77,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}會錯意了也沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.98,0:01:31.77,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}和你一起就是幸福 這樣想著卻不告訴你
